aiSLCAlias.contactinfo: Engineering MIB Administrator Postal: Applied Innovation Inc. 5800 Innovation Drive Dublin, Ohio 43017-3271 Tel: 614-798-2000 Fax: 614-798-1770 Email: snmp@aiinet.com
aiSLCAlias.description: MIB module for SLCs with alias translation ability.

aiSLCAliasTable.name: aiSLCAliasTable
aiSLCAliasTable.description: Table of aliases stored in the SLC, indexed by alias name. Rows are managed with the SNMPv2 RowStatus mechanism. All strings in this table may be up to 300 characters long, except the description, which may be up to 80.

aislcaliAliasName.name: aislcaliAliasName
aislcaliAliasName.description: Name of the alias to which this table row applies. Maximum length is 255 characters.

aislcaliRowStatus.name: aislcaliRowStatus
aislcaliRowStatus.description: Status of this row, as defined by SNMPv2.

aislcaliDescription.name: aislcaliDescription
aislcaliDescription.description: Textual description of this alias. Maximum length is 80 characters.

aislcaliDestination.name: aislcaliDestination
aislcaliDestination.description: Destination of this alias. Maximum length is 255 characters.

aislcaliShowInDestMenu.name: aislcaliShowInDestMenu
aislcaliShowInDestMenu.description: Show this alias in the destination menu.

aislcaliCallingAddr.name: aislcaliCallingAddr
aislcaliCallingAddr.description: Address of the entity calling this alias. Maximum length is 255 characters.

aislcaliCalledAddr.name: aislcaliCalledAddr
aislcaliCalledAddr.description: Address called by this alias. Maximum length is 255 characters.

aislcaliCallData.name: aislcaliCallData
aislcaliCallData.description: String used for SLC-dependent features. Maximum length is 255 characters.

aislcaliCallingProto.name: aislcaliCallingProto
aislcaliCallingProto.description: Protocol used by the entity calling this alias. Maximum length is 255 characters.

aislcaliCalledProto.name: aislcaliCalledProto
aislcaliCalledProto.description: Protocol used for a call placed by this alias. Maximum length is 255 characters.

aislcaliAppString.name: aislcaliAppString
aislcaliAppString.description: String used for SLC-dependent features. Maximum length is 255 characters.

aislcaliAltRoute.name: aislcaliAltRoute
aislcaliAltRoute.description: Name of an alternative alias the SLC can use. Maximum length is 255 characters.
